    <string name="help_title">HELP</string>
    <string name="help_text">
        Fusion Chess is a new game that based on Chinese Chess.
        It gives Rooks,Knights, Cannons and Pawns another use on the basis of the traditional rules of Chinese Chess.\n\n

        [CHARIOT], [HORSE], [CANNON] and [PAWN] in Fusion Chess can remix with each other, for example,\n\n

        [HORSE] and [CHARIOT] make [HORSE_CHARIOT].\n\n

        From the fusion of two chess pieces, a chess of Fusion Chess could have the power of both pieces,
        meanwhile, a mixed chess can also be taken apart to enhance the motility of pieces to avoid more loss.
        The fusion and separation of pieces makes the game more flexible and more nervous,
        so that the game could be more interesting.\n\n

        In traditional Chinese Chess, [PAWN] can only go straight but not go side before cross the river,
        it was saved in the Fusion Chess, it keeps some limit to the pieces that have [PAWN],
        in order that there are no unexpected cases appear.\n\n

        If you want to know more about the game, please try it,
        the Fusion Chess will give you a fantastic experience.\n\n\n

        Producer:Keshi, jjtx, Cindy\n
        E-mail:823424123@163.com\n
    </string>
    
